{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo_tutorials/pullrequests/92/comments/3238857.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gazebo_tutorials/diff/osrf/gazebo_tutorials:451f5e1426d9..f3b586327ee3?path=gazebojs_pubsub%2Ftutorial.md"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo_tutorials/pull-requests/92/_/diff#comment-3238857"}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 92, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo_tutorials/pullrequests/92.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo_tutorials/pull-requests/92"}}, "title": "GazeboJs : NodeJs bindings for Gazebo"}, "content": {"raw": "For me this only works sometimes. I found out if I add a little delay it always works though:\n\n\n```\n#!javascript\n\nsetTimeout(function (){\n  gazebo.publish(type, topic , msg);\n  console.log('\\npublished!');\n},10);\n```\n", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>For me this only works sometimes. I found out if I add a little delay it always works though:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite language-javascript\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"nx\">setTimeout</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"kd\">function</span> <span class=\"p\">(){</span>\n  <span class=\"nx\">gazebo</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"nx\">publish</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nx\">type</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"nx\">topic</span> <span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"nx\">msg</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n  <span class=\"nx\">console</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"nx\">log</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;\\npublished!&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n<span class=\"p\">},</span><span class=\"mi\">10</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n</pre></div>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2014-09-26T23:38:02.610430+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Louise Poubel", "uuid": "{5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4}", "links": {"self": {"href": "h